69d77401ef6980a204dde5cf65df6.webm?t=1752805196\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222530/extras/dad69d77401ef6980a204dde5cf65df6.mp4?t=1752805196\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222530/extras/3e634f5abf4e78a709338184336dc802.poster.avif?t=1752805196\" width=800 height=457 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222530/extras/3e634f5abf4e78a709338184336dc802.webm?t=1752805196\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222530/extras/38a9212f20bee5d4bdddfbecab902877.avif?t=1752805196\" width=327 height=66 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You awaken in an unfamiliar place, your memory completely gone. <br><strong>\"Irene\"</strong> a young woman, tends to your amnesia with an unsettlingly meticulous care.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But something feels off. Can you truly trust her?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > you can only say one thing: \"Understood.\" or Silent <br>Trapped in a small room with no memory, <br>Doesn’t that strike you as strange?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Uncover the truth and find your way out before it's too late.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222530/extras/b90369994c34407c6de68fc77dc54259.avif?t=1752805196\" width=327 height=66 /></span><strong> </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> <br>    <br>👁️‍🗨️ Puzzles and Exploration   </strong>Investigate and search for clues in every room. Solving puzzles unlocks new areas and accelerates the story, heightening tension with each step forward.<strong>  <br>   <br>👁️‍🗨️Butterfly Effect </strong>Some action take impacts the story. Will your choices lead to salvation or ruin?  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>👁️‍🗨️3 Endings  </strong>The ending depends on your actions throughout the story. Miss a crucial detail, and you might lose the chance to uncover the truth.<strong>   <br>  </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong> </strong><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3222530/extras/e1cec920a2777bbdc8fabb1e945309d2.avif?t=1752805196\" width=639 height=160 /></span><strong></strong></p>",
